{"type": "article", "id": 31902, "title": "她为小朋友设计的家具，就像是一个农场｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-06T23:14:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3208, "name": "Normann Copenhagen"}, {"id": 31535, "name": "Cube 44"}, {"id": 32507, "name": "kaschkasch"}, {"id": 32508, "name": "SIPS Productions"}, {"id": 32509, "name": "LYRA"}, {"id": 31539, "name": "Pavel Vetrov"}, {"id": 32510, "name": "Roee Magdassi"}, {"id": 32511, "name": "Nataša Njegovanović"}, {"id": 32512, "name": "Michal Slovák"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 170, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160906234937j3wPlWvO9pZ5qbu8.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Edge by Roee Magdassi</h3><p>像拎提灯一样移动一张桌子会是什么样？在今年的法国科隆园艺用品展（<a href=\"http://www.spogagafa.com/spogagafa/index-2.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">spoga+gafa</a>）的 <a href=\"http://www.spogagafa.com/spogagafa/Landing-Pages/Contest-young-star-garden-unique/index.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">unique youngstars</a> 竞赛上，特拉维夫的设计师 <a href=\"http://www.magdassi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Roee Magdassi</a> 就带来了两款附有把手的 Edge 圆桌。当把手平放在桌面上时，它又成为了一道立体的边缘。虽然它们的结构并不复杂，但以这种独特的方式将功能与美感结合在一起的设计着实让人眼前一亮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235226CemRQEbpI0P9ZwTd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.282396\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609062352260IYoqQgCWjHDFU5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609062352262uGzcQL1PHCEVfWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235226QE79vOBMYAH0Lon2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.614914\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235227g0RNp3OMWjQtSoP5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609062352261c2sjGTaWBhtn5pJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Avila by Nataša Njegovanović</h3><p>在为孩子们设计家具时，很多设计师的都会参考小动物的造型，来自克罗地亚的 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/natasanjegovanovic\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nataša Njegovanović</a> 也不例外。在她设计的这套名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/35871067/Avlia-Furniture-System-for-Children\" rel=\"nofollow\">Avila</a> 的家具系列中，奶牛桌、小狗凳、小猪储物箱为孩子们提供了一个既能学习又能游戏的空间。除了这些家具之外，Njegovanović 还设计了猫咪脚踏车和小鸡铅笔盒，让孩子们能够完全沉浸在这个可爱而统一的环境当中，与各种物件进行互动，从而激发他们的想象力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235010Rv4UKQJT5ZqMlWc9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.066015\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235010H6bXEBc9GQUganPW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235010ZQ9h8rfy2tJd3s0L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235011zGM3pCgRYjZhDr0y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.669927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235011F60U4XeBbOWGZSQt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235011RxA1qriNsn7EMbo6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668704\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Proportioner by SIPS Productions Inc.</h3><p>以黄金比例绘制的图案或是设计的物品总是能够带给人一种和谐的视觉享受，然而想要发现或是自己也尝试一次黄金分割并不是一件容易的事。为了帮助人们发现和打造黄金比例，加拿大公司 <a href=\"http://www.secretsinplainsight.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SIPS Productions</a> 最近就推出了一款实用的黄金比例测径器 Proportioner，测量范围在 24 到 320 毫米之间。由于胶合板不够稳定，设计师最后选择了胡桃木作为材料，中间用来测定黄金比例的组件通过带磁性的铰链与传统的测径器连接在一起，可以随时拆卸组装。在不使用的时候，Proportioner 还能放在配套的支架上，成为一件精致的桌面摆设。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/secretsinplainsight/the-proportioner-golden-ratio-calipers\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 33 加元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090623514989vHfGRwsz7DL5um.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235152tEjJYiL0GcpSzo8R.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235154FMAq3JI6tkONrQub.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235149uPhQskRtcO3Djzal.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.319118\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235149ZIUplODA1XBxJref.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.517647\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235149xpnRiwJQB5VWG89m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.514706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Horizon Mirrors by kaschkasch</h3><p>在巴黎家居装饰博览会秋展上，丹麦品牌 <a href=\"http://www.normann-copenhagen.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Normann Copenhagen</a> 展出了由德国科隆 <a href=\"http://kaschkasch.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">kaschkasch</a> 工作室设计的 Horizon 镜子系列。这些根据海平面为灵感设计的镜子配有一个金属隔板，同时还能当作储物架使用。通过镜子的反射，Horizon 营造出了一种独特的视觉效果，兼具了实用性与美感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609062351345ksQAqrYTBK8wt4X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.226054\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235134EsU0gTJx8pkWo5j9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235134sIOXqB1QRMcNu5VC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.448333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235134NtpIxk15uhUlq63G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235134UsIaA42lB50nJdOw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.388333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235135CaAbmTIQ9JMiwP7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.171667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Horizon-Hanger by Pavel Vetrov</h3><p>Horizon 是乌克兰设计师 <a href=\"http://www.pavelvetrov.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pavel Vetrov</a> 为 <a href=\"http://www.cube44.com.ua/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Cube 44</a> 所设计的一个家具系列，我们此前介绍过其中的一款<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/31034.html\">书架</a>。最近擅长极简风格的 Vetrov 为这个系列设计了几款由黑色金属框和木制隔板构成的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/42359809/Horizon-Hanger\" rel=\"nofollow\">衣架</a>，干净利落的线条前后交错，同时又保持了一种微妙的一体感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235118xO4QoU8anFdvZsjW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016090623511969U1CvMwsSh7XYNH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235120VvFgKpRHJuPYWOh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235120VOR8erlAiHsIUzg6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235119LF4ohOlfWKw6YmHP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235119lTRrDb9PiSgJFcQm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LYRA by Michal Slovák</h3><p>斯洛文尼亚巧克力品牌 <a href=\"http://www.lyrachocolate.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LYRA</a> 最近委托设计师 <a href=\"http://www.michalslovak.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Michal Slovák</a> 重新设计了旗下数款巧克力包装。在新版中，Slovák 通过牛皮纸盒将几个系列统一起来，并在侧面通过数字进行标注。针对以可可豆产地划分的巧克力系列，Slovák 不仅为它们分配了不同的颜色以示区别，还将它们的信息以邮戳的方式印刷在包装上，看上去就像是一张张来自非洲中南部的明信片。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235025cfFpv0TBPQDVHor9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235025PdA0J7bkYNzM3Llr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235025vqd42h0froUxK6yI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609062350263QLb4ZnJBrHXcw50.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235026oDwHIFAEJR9zGNmC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160906235026IZpw0GD6yHgnis8X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}